<h2 id="oh-my-a-missing-inversedbt">Oh my, a Missing inversedBt <a class="headerlink" href="easy-collection-filtering#oh-my-a-missing-inversedbt" title="Permalink to this headline"><i class="fa fa-link" aria-hidden="true"></i></a></h2>
<p>First, see that red label on the web debug toolbar? Click it, and scroll down.
It's a mapping warning:</p>
<blockquote><p>The field <code>User#studiedGenuses</code> property is on the inverse side of a bidirectional
relationship, but the association on blah-blah-blah does not contain the required
<code>inversedBy</code>.</p>
</blockquote>
<p>In human-speak, this says that my <code>User</code> correctly has a <code>studiedGenuses</code> property
with a <code>mappedBy</code> option...</p>
