<h2 id="bad-field-type-mapping">Bad Field Type Mapping! <a class="headerlink" href="easy-collection-filtering#bad-field-type-mapping" title="Permalink to this headline"><i class="fa fa-link" aria-hidden="true"></i></a></h2>
<p>The second thing I need to fix is this <code>yearsStudied</code> field. When PhpStorm generated
the annotation for us, it used <code>type="string"</code>... and I forgot to fix it! Change
it to <code>type="integer"</code>:</p>
