            </tr>

        </tbody>
    </table>
</div>
</p>
<p>This will loop over <em>all</em> of the genus scientists and return a new <code>ArrayCollection</code>
that only contains the ones that have studied for more than 20 years. It's perfect!</p>
<p>To print this in the template, let's add a new line, then
<code>{{ genus.expertScientists|length }}</code> and then "experts":</p>
